{"tid":1620530,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港戒嚴！行政會議通過引用緊急法　午夜實施","createTime":"2019-10-04T10:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:45:18.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dc0c72dc165571cd5a63d0b87ecb680097f0724d","tid":1620530,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"香港戒嚴！行政會議通過引用緊急法　午夜實施<br />\n<br />\n香港特首會以及行政會議剛剛通過，引用緊急法訂立「禁蒙面法」，從今日午夜起實施，形同宣告香港進入戒嚴狀態，特首林鄭月娥下午3點將舉行記者會對外說明。<br />\n<br />\n而在消息傳出的同時，香港金融重鎮中環已經有上萬人上街示威遊行，民間團體明天下午3點並發起「全民蒙面遊行」，爭取國際關注緊急法。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bcc.com.tw/newsView.3649656?fbclid=IwAR2uc7qaVYuU82TUwOeezW5JslAyOkTiTVFDowaJZjaa2UKfphamh2r_lQg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcc.com.tw%2FnewsView.3649656%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2uc7qaVYuU82TUwOeezW5JslAyOkTiTVFDowaJZjaa2UKfphamh2r_lQg&d=x%2FNl6Ahg6Nkeqb8F8iTJG5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=0aa88756\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bcc.com.tw/newsView.3649656?fbclid=IwAR2uc7qaVYuU82TUwOeezW5JslAyOkTiTVFDowaJZjaa2UKfphamh2r_lQg</a>"},{"pid":"3be4b22f590e119316425e95b953ee72ab2e2b72","tid":1620530,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"林鄭攬炒"},{"pid":"362a3c1494152aaf5c383d85cde4df71bd6032f7","tid":1620530,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"用緊急法又唔係緊急狀態係咩玩法"},{"pid":"f0c486f85f64338c5be4aa30c93365887755a91a","tid":1620530,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"362a3c1494152aaf5c383d85cde4df71bd6032f7","tid":1620530,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"用緊急法又唔係緊急狀態係咩玩法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:45:18.000Z","msg":"代表佢話咩就咩"}]}